{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_13_level_main_13-15_beg","storyGroup":"main_13","storySort":164,"storyDependence":"main_13_level_main_13-15_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"13-17","storyName":"谁来倾诉","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"大战在即，赫德雷，伊内丝与W畅想未来，赫德雷提出萨卡兹们不能否定特雷西斯，与W争吵。之前下落不明的巨兽骸骨终于归来，众人开始进攻。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_13-15_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_13-15","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":20,"next":22,"characters":["萨卡兹？","赫德雷","W","伊内丝","推进之王","希勒少尉","戴菲恩","Logos","脊椎守卫","阿米娅"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"stopmusic","id":4},{"type":"dialog","id":5},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"charslot","id":9},{"type":"dialog","id":10},{"type":"interlude","maskid":"ui_cutin_mask_vertical","style":"1","size":"500, 720","offset":"120,0","channel":"2","id":11},{"type":"2","channel":"2","name":"43_g4_spinestops_ex","afrom":"0","ato":"1","aduration":"2","sfrom":"1.9,1.9","sto":"1.9,1.9","sduration":"0","id":12},{"type":"1","channel":"2","slot":"m","offset":"120,20","name":"cutin_char_3","sfrom":"1.1,1.1","sto":"1.1,1.1","aduration":"2","block":"false","id":13},{"type":"1","channel":"2","slot":"m","pfrom":"120,20","pto":"170,20","duration":"40","id":14},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":15},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"sticker","id":17,"multi":"true","text":"自我们与厄尔苏拉的战斗过后，那座山洞的防守就越发严密，W和她的炸弹们帮我们撤离了一次，但未必能奏效第二次。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":18,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我们没有再次成功接近那里。但我也确信，那具“漂流的骸骨”，自那之后，也从未归来。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":19},{"type":"sticker","id":20,"multi":"true","text":"直到，我们所有人都做了同一个梦。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":21},{"type":"interlude","channel":"2","clear":"true","duration":"2","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":23},{"type":"sticker","id":24,"multi":"true","text":"灰白的城市被火焰吞没，城墙破碎，焦炭般的尸骸充塞每一个角落。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":25,"multi":"true","text":"\\n直到我们睁开眼睛，那座城市仍未随梦境离去。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":26},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":27},{"type":"dialog","id":28},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":29},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":30},{"type":"charslot","id":31},{"type":"dialog","id":32},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":33},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":34},{"type":"sticker","id":35,"multi":"true","text":"火焰之路践踏过每一个聚落，每一个氏族。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":36,"multi":"true","text":"\\n曾经被称为卡兹戴尔的地方已经不复存在，只剩下余火与废墟。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":37,"multi":"true","text":"\\n绝望的巨人跪地哭泣。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":38},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹？","text":"（古老的萨卡兹语）魔王死了。","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹？","text":"（古老的萨卡兹语）魔王杀死了魔王。","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹？","text":"（古老的萨卡兹语）为什么，不该是这样——","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹？","text":"（古老的萨卡兹语）我们的城市，卡兹戴尔......","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹？","text":"（古老的萨卡兹语）这会是诅咒！这会是刻印进王冠的诅咒——","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹？","text":"（古老的萨卡兹语）这会是......一切灾难的开始——","id":45},{"type":"dialog","id":46},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":47},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":48},{"type":"sticker","id":49,"multi":"true","text":"那只巨兽，回来了。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":50},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":51},{"type":"dialog","id":52},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":53},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1d/Avg_bg_bg_coldforest.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":54},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":55},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":56,"musicid":1},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"明天一早，进攻就会开始。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8b/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"推进之王和她的“典范军”将负责外围的牵制，我们，罗德岛的小兔子和女妖需要深入那座停靠站。","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8b/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"凯尔希那老女人呢？这么危险的行动，她只派我们送死，自己不出出力？","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"她的伤还没有痊愈，阿斯卡纶会保证她和博士的安全，他们都会留在后方。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/66/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"罗德岛在不久前曾遭到赦罪师的袭击，那些人想夺取小兔子的那顶王冠。","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/66/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"哼，王冠。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......赫德雷，你没和那些维多利亚人说实话。","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"如果你的计划成功了，我们回到了卡兹戴尔，你打算干什么？","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"哪怕是和你当了朋友的维多利亚人，恐怕也不会接受你连“战犯”和“被卷进战争的萨卡兹”一起打包带走这件事。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"别告诉我你信誓旦旦地告诉我们“会带萨卡兹们回家”，自己却没考虑过这个问题。","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"比如，去卡兹戴尔那座地窖里的大学，给这些从战场上回来的家伙开一门，呵，“反思历史”的课？","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/66/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"不。","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我也许会在卡兹戴尔开个识字班，让萨卡兹以后少几个W这样的文盲。","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"啊？","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"我没听错吧？赫德雷居然在这么严肃的话题上也能顺着伊内丝的话开玩笑了？","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"咋了，讨好曼弗雷德将军让你情商高了一点点？","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"哼——","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"“战争结束，回到卡兹戴尔。”多可笑，我们居然在这里幻想这些事情。","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f4/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"我们是佣兵，我们不会别的。","id":98,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"你是个可爱的卡普里尼，伊内丝，你说不定可以去莱塔尼亚，给那些住在塔里的高高在上的贵族们当家教。","id":100,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"就教......我想想，教怎么在战场上保持秀发靓丽，怎么样？","id":102,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3d/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"不怎么样。","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f4/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......","id":106,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"你在发什么呆？马上就要开战了。","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d1/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"不，我只是......","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/be/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":111},{"type":"dialog","id":112},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"sticker","id":115,"multi":"true","text":"伊内丝的目光微微瞥向了我的脚下。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":116,"multi":"true","text":"\\n她又在看我的影子。我的影子现在是什么状态？","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":117,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我也不知道。我确实极少在行动前这么......平静。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":118},{"type":"sticker","id":119,"multi":"true","text":"平静使得我有余力去想很多事情。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":120,"multi":"true","text":"\\n一些，小事。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":121},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":122},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我记得，以前你说过，你打算开一家店，在卡兹戴尔。","id":124,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"那是因为当时我们没有销赃的地方。","id":126,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......是啊。","id":128,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......","id":130,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我在识字班挣的第一笔学费，做你的本钱怎么样？","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"我很怀疑识字班能挣到多少钱。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f4/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"不过，绑一个莱塔尼亚的贵族家教能挣的赎金倒是不会少，起码比十个雇佣兵的头值钱。","id":136,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"先等我们真的回了家再说吧。","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"是啊。","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"你的精神状态让我怀疑你能不能胜任接下来的任务。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"被幻境啊法阵啊之类的折磨傻了？","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":145},{"type":"dialog","id":146},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":147},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":148},{"type":"sticker","id":149,"multi":"true","text":"可能确实是这样。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":150,"multi":"true","text":"\\n平静到极点的时刻，某些不安的触须开始令人心肝刺挠，令人犹豫不决。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":151,"multi":"true","text":"\\n在我自己都感到诧异的思绪之中，我找到了我焦急的原因。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":152},{"type":"sticker","id":153,"multi":"true","text":"我担心她们不认同我。关于我的......","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":154,"multi":"true","text":"\\n一些，想法。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":155,"multi":"true","text":"\\n可不得不说。箭在弦上了。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":156},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":157},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"别理这个一向多愁善感的傻子了。","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"时间不等人。等我们宰了那个血魔，宰了特雷西斯，你们大可以回到卡兹戴尔慢慢商量爱巢的装修。","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......特雷西斯。","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/66/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"这件事我想了很久，W。接下来我要说的也许你无法接受，但我还是得告诉你。","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"哈，在开打前给人泼冷水？","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"确实如此。","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我们不能杀特雷西斯，起码不能在此时此刻，由萨卡兹处决他。","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"——","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"伊内丝说得对，你确实是被幻象折磨傻了——","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"杀了他，卡兹戴尔将不复存在。","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/66/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"无论是在现在，还是在战争结束后的相当一段时间里，他都必须以摄政王的身份被记载......乃至，被部分人歌颂。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/66/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#13$1","focus":"m","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......你疯了吗？","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#13$1","focus":"m","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"在这件事上我不想开玩笑。","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我们仍要停止这场战争，我并未改变先前的看法。","id":185,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"但特雷西斯已经把自己浇筑成了萨卡兹未来的基石。","id":187,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"卡兹戴尔不能再遭受一次分裂，这场战争......也不能结束于萨卡兹的又一次背叛和内战的开始。","id":189,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"记得我之前说的计划吗？我们需要的是在所有人得知他的死亡之前，让这片战场上的萨卡兹们撤离维多利亚。","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"萨卡兹的失败一旦公开，特雷西斯的威慑一旦不复存在——那么，会发生什么？","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"公爵们会肆无忌惮地屠杀维多利亚境内的萨卡兹，报复会延伸至核心圈的其他国家，每一个文明都有正当借口......把萨卡兹赶尽杀绝。","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"然后组织一支联军，合理又正义、迅速又果决地......瓜分特蕾西娅和特雷西斯留下的所有遗产。","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你想不到吗？","id":201,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"说真的，我一点都不在乎特雷西斯的死会有什么后果，我需要的只是他的“死”。","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/33/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"联军？杀死萨卡兹？他们不原本就在做这样的事吗？","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/33/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"难道特雷西斯一死，魔族佬们就连反抗的欲望也集体消散了？","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/33/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"嘁。我不会，我也不信。","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/33/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"是他派刺客杀了特蕾西娅，自诩为王，把所有人拖进今天这步田地。","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/33/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"我们不需要为了他的卡兹戴尔，委身于他的——","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/33/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"别以为自己能置身事外，W。","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":216},{"type":"dialog","id":217},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":218},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":219},{"type":"sticker","id":220,"multi":"true","text":"我本以为我会以更激烈的情绪斥责她。斥责W这个......可怜人。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":221},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":222},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你还以为自己不过是一个佣兵？","id":224,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你带来了多少人？从整合运动到现在，你聚集了多少萨卡兹？","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你现在背着他们的命。","id":228,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":229},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"我他妈不在乎！","id":231,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":232},{"type":"dialog","id":233},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":234},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"sticker","id":236,"multi":"true","text":"但W动摇了。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":237,"multi":"true","text":"\\n我太熟悉她了。她并非什么都没想，她也并非一个真的不在乎部下的领袖。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":238,"multi":"true","text":"\\n起码客观上，真的有很多雇佣兵愿意跟这个疯子混。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":239},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":240},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你必须在乎。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你觉得，你只要和以前一样，杀杀人，埋埋炸弹就行了？","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你现在是那些萨卡兹的领袖，你必须要想清楚，你该怎么处置他们的希望。","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你必须想清楚，这些命，对你意味着什么。","id":248,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"我——","id":250,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/33/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......","id":252,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/33/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":253},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"charslot","id":256},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5a/Avg_43_i11.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":257},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"不止特雷西斯——","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"别忘了，还有特蕾西娅。","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"所以，从所有角度来说，我们都......只能是他们的继承者，是他们理念的延伸。","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"他们两人，才是萨卡兹能团结起来的原因。","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"那不是真的特蕾西娅。","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"那不过是特雷西斯造出来的冒牌货，他骗不过我。","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"W。","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"正视你自己。","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"你以为你是谁——","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你不能接受特蕾西娅的死，你习惯了当巴别塔的影子。","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"甚至......","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"住嘴。","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你觉得有阿米娅走在你的前面。你觉得，她才是特蕾西娅选定的继承人，“魔王”才该考虑这些事情。","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你把她看作另一个特蕾西娅，你觉得，只需要追随“魔王”就好。","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"住嘴！你在故意恶心我吗？！","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......你觉得自己不配继承什么。","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......开什么玩笑，你自以为你了解我吗？你真把自己当成教育我的人了，赫德雷？","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"你也只是个雇佣兵，比我高不到哪里去。你就能自诩为什么什么继承者了？","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"呸，恶心死了！小兔子？还我追随她？","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"她就是个机缘巧合之下才被——","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"——才被特蕾西娅选中，成了阻止整合运动和塔露拉，今天又打进了伦蒂尼姆的罗德岛领导人。","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"那么你呢？","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"W，特蕾西娅对于你到底意味着什么？","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"只是个曾经让你有个容身之所的遥远象征，那个具体的有血有肉的殿下，还是——她所代表的路？","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......我......","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"“为了这片大地......能够安稳入眠。”","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......啧。","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"所以......我才会说，她是假的。","id":287},{"type":"dialog","id":288},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":290},{"type":"charslot","id":291},{"type":"image","id":292},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......","id":295,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......","id":297,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......","id":299,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"......伊内丝，你是怎么忍着这么久没宰了他的？","id":301,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"因为我很少骗自己。","id":303,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f4/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"嘁。少来。","id":305,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"别瞎操心了，赫德雷。","id":307,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"我知道自己该做什么。这次就不以动摇军心的名义宰了你，你该给我磕个头。","id":309,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"好好打磨你的剑，准备好明天的战斗吧。","id":311,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":312},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walkfast","volume":"0.7","id":313},{"type":"charslot","duration":"2","id":314},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":315},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"唉......还是逃开了。","id":317,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"你真的觉得，她能成个像样的领袖？","id":319,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"她组织起了一大批雇佣兵。","id":321,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"呵呵，真的是“雇佣兵”吗？","id":323,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"W能有几个钱雇他们？她做的事又能给他们赚几个钱？","id":325,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/95/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"那么，那些跟着W的人，到底是因为什么跟着她？","id":327,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"不管她自己怎么说，为特蕾西娅报仇也好，追杀当年刺杀的参与者也罢，还是说自己什么都没想，只是一路狂轰滥炸——","id":329,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"她都确实......已经走在了那条路上。","id":331,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......跟着她混的人真可怜。","id":333,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"但其实很多人都忘了，她还很年轻。她有很大的......进步空间。","id":335,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"但愿吧。","id":337,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/66/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"还有，第一笔钱给你开店，不是玩笑。","id":339,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......我知道。","id":341,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":342},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":343},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":344},{"type":"dialog","id":345},{"type":"charslot","id":346},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":347},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/73/Avg_bg_bg_barracks.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":348},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":349},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":350},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$batmeeting_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_batmeeting_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":351,"musicid":2},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"“典范军”已经整备完成了。","id":353,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"伦蒂尼姆自救军的一部分成员，自愿加入了我们的队伍中。","id":355,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1070_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"嗯，加上我们这一路收拢的原本属于各个公爵的残兵、想要参与战斗的难民和自救军的这些民兵，我们大概有了六七个连的兵力。","id":357,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2e/Avg_avg_npc_1070_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1070_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"推进之王，我们最好正式建立“典范军”的军制，任命军官，这样我们的指挥系统才......","id":359,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2e/Avg_avg_npc_1070_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"希勒少尉，这支队伍不是一支真的军队。“维多利亚的军队”。","id":361,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"确实，我们有一些士兵......","id":363,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"但除去你和戴菲恩带领的温德米尔公爵的残部，其余的只是想要战斗的普通人。工人，农民，商人，当然，还有街头流氓。","id":365,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"如果我们把他们强行编进一两个战斗小组里面，再给他们塞一把武器，就要他们听命于军官们的指挥，我们和那些公爵有什么区别？","id":367,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"“典范军”是个很好的名头。但我认为它应该给人们带来纯粹的希望。","id":369,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"或者别把话说那么大，给人们带来一点公爵们的高速军舰带不来的，虚无缥缈的事物。","id":371,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fa/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"所以说......","id":373,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"典范军不该是由手握国剑的王位继承人统领的英雄军队。我相当反感这些名头。","id":375,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/03/Avg_avgnew_112_siege_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1070_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"可是，我们该怎么组织军事行动？","id":377,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_1070_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"要说军事行动，我们的队伍里也有相当部分的人连正规的军事训练都没有接受过。","id":379,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"入乡随俗吧。","id":381,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"就像我们在切特雷镇做的那样，就像自救军在伦蒂尼姆做的那样。","id":383,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dc/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我们还是和自己熟悉的人，用自己喜欢的方式，去杀那些萨卡兹。","id":385,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dc/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"......无意冒犯，萨卡兹们。","id":387,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......","id":389,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1072_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Logos","text":"无妨。我不在乎。","id":391,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_1072_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1072_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Logos","text":"仪式已被终止，但残留在萨卡兹血脉中的赐福，并没有彻底消弭。","id":393,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_1072_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1072_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Logos","text":"伦蒂尼姆的方向......古老的巫术在翻腾。","id":395,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_1072_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1072_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Logos","text":"我们的死敌有着不可告人的目的，但他们所表露出的紧迫仓促，反而能成为突破的助力。","id":397,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_1072_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我们会加倍注意。","id":399,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dc/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"那么......","id":401,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":402},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"让我们抢回那根香骨头吧。","id":403,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":404},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":405},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":406},{"type":"dialog","id":407},{"type":"charslot","id":408},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":409},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/eb/Avg_bg_43_g4_spinestops_ex.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":410},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":411},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":412},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$exciting_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_exciting02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":413,"musicid":3},{"type":"dialog","id":414},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_explosion","volume":"0.9","id":415},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"4","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":416},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":417},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":418},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":419},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":420},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":421},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":422},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":423},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#9$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":424},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":425},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"计划很成功，那帮维多利亚人的进攻确实为我们引开了一部分这里的军队。","id":426,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"我们进来了，它确实在这里。","id":428,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":429},{"type":"charslot","id":430},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","volume":"1","id":431},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":432},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"脊椎守卫","text":"你们，是上次的那几个萨卡兹？你们怎么——","id":434,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"脊椎守卫","text":"你们和维多利亚人，一起进攻这里？","id":436,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......抱歉了。","id":438,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8b/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":439},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":440},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":441},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.8","id":442},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":443},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":444},{"type":"charslot","id":445},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","volume":"1","id":446},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":447},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":448},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","volume":"1","id":449},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":450},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":451},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":452},{"type":"charslot","id":453},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"脊椎守卫","text":"杀死这些叛徒！杀死这些萨卡兹的叛徒！","id":455,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":456},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"厄尔苏拉没有亲自迎接我们。","id":457,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8b/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4087_ines_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"Logos猜得对，看来她确实正忙得不可开交。","id":459,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4087_ines_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":460},{"type":"charslot","id":461},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_explosion","volume":"0.9","id":462},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"4","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":463},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":464},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":465},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":466},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":467},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":468},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":469},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":470},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":471},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"哈——上次你们没让我跟进来，这可真是个大家伙！","id":472,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_412_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":473},{"type":"dialogue","name":"W","text":"我能把它炸成两截吗？","id":474,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_412_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4088_hodrer_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":475},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"不行，跟上队伍。","id":476,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8b/Avg_avg_4088_hodrer_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":477},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"马上登上脊椎，控制它的操纵者！","id":478,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1072_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Logos","text":"......","id":480,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_1072_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1072_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":481},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Logos","text":"阿米娅。","id":482,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_1072_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"嗯。我感觉到了。","id":484,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":485},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"他在这里。","id":486,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_avg_npc_394_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":487},{"type":"dialog","id":488},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":489},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":490},{"type":"sticker","id":491,"multi":"true","text":"我顺着女妖的眼神望向岩顶投下的影子。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":492,"multi":"true","text":"\\n一丝血腥味闯进我的鼻腔。","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":493},{"type":"sticker","id":494,"multi":"true","text":"这具骸骨......它有血管吗？","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":495},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":496},{"type":"dialog","id":497},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":498},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":499},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":500},{"type":"character","id":501},{"type":"image","id":502}],"characters":["萨卡兹？","赫德雷","W","伊内丝","推进之王","希勒少尉","戴菲恩","Logos","脊椎守卫","阿米娅"]}